Free Shipping Orders Over $89


We offer free USPS shipping on all domestic orders over $89.
                                        Shipping on all international orders is $34.99 via USPS.
                                    

                                        All orders are
                                        shipped from Orlando Florida.
                                    










×
Rx Lens Guarantee



                                        We realize many consumers are not totally comfortable with
                                        ordering prescription lenses online. Simply Eyeglasses wants to replace
                                        reluctance with confidence.
                                    

                                        Once you receive your prescription lenses from
                                        us, you have 30 days to try them. If for any reason you are not satisfied
                                        with your lenses during that time frame, simply contact customer service. We
                                        will remake your lenses to your complete satisfaction or offer you a 100%
                                        refund.
                                    

                                        Simply Eyeglasses does not charge a restocking fee on lenses. At
                                        Simply Eyeglasses 100% refund means 100%. In addition, we will gladly remake
                                        your lenses for any change made by your physician on your prescription
                                        within that same 30 day period. Our goal is complete customer
                                        satisfaction.
                                    










×
No Sales Tax Except Florida



                                        No sales tax on prescription eyewear of any kind purchased and
                                        shipped to any location. This includes prescription sunglasses.
                                    

                                        There is no
                                        sales tax on non-prescription eyewear or frames outside the state of
                                        Florida. Since we are based in Florida, we must collect sales tax on
                                        non-prescription sunglasses and frame only orders shipped to Florida
                                        locations.
                                    










×
Price Match Guarantee


Simply Eyeglasses will price match any current U.S. available
                                        frame or sunglasses on reliable U.S. based optical only websites. We do not
                                        price match Amazon, EBay, or brick and mortar establishments. We must be
                                        able to contact the competitor via phone and verify the authenticity of the
                                        product in question. Competitor's pricing must be above our cost. Simply
                                        Eyeglasses will also price match prescription lenses. Above rules apply. Not
                                        all sites use the same lenses. Simply Eyeglasses reserves the right to apply
                                        price match to comparable lenses. Please consider shipping and handling
                                        charges when comparing pricing. If for whatever reason Simply Eyeglasses
                                        cannot match a price, we are always willing to work with consumers on
                                        alternative prices or products.























